metadata.description: Use Generative adversarial network to create art through machine learning and social engineering," says team member Jonathan Martin. , which he first presented at ICML 2013 in San Diego, California. His aim is "to build creative systems that perform an experiment based on a pre-existing set of rules." This work includes the use for both artists themselves as well others including researchers studying their artistic style, which takes advantage many methods from computer vision.
